com.polarion.platform.service.repository

Interface IResourceProperties


  • public interface IResourceProperties
    System properties of given resource.

    The meaning of last changed in connection with resource with older revision is dependent on implementation of IRepositoryService.

    Author:
    Stepan Roh, Polarion Software
